thread.title: JW

author: JW
title: JW
text: The PhysioRoom stocked what I was looking for plus many other items that I don't need to buy at the moment; there were good product descriptions. Ordering was straightforward and the price competitive. I was a little disappointed there were no express delivery options but the consignment arrived next day (earlier than predicted), so a faster option was unnecessary. I am happy to use The PhysioRoom again.
